@TITLE "snap2tzx(1)ĀmanualĀpage"
 @{" " link "'#toc'/MAIN"}Table of Contents

 @{" " link "'#toc0'/MAIN"}Name snap2tzx - Convert ZX Spectrum snapshot to .tzx tape images @{" " link "'#toc1'/MAIN"}Synopsis @{"b"}snap2tzx@{"ub"} [-1 @{"i"}string@{"ui"}]@{"i"}@{"ui"} [-2 @{"i"}string@{"ui"}]@{"i"}@{"ui"} [-b @{"i"}colour@{"ui"}]@{"i"}@{"ui"} [-g @{"i"}string@{"ui"}]@{"i"}@{"ui"} [-l @{"i"}string@{"ui"}]@{"i"}@{"ui"} [-o @{"i"}filename@{"ui"}]@{"i"}@{"ui"} [-r] [-s @{"i"}speed@{"ui"}]@{"i"}@{"ui"} [-v] [-$ @{"i"}filename@{"ui"}]@{"i"}@{"ui"} @{"i"}snapshot@{"ui"} 

@{" " link "'#toc2'/MAIN"}Description snap2tzx converts a ZX Spectrum snapshot into a .tzx tape image. @{" " link "'#toc3'/MAIN"}Options -1 @{"i"}string@{"ui"} causes @{"i"}string@{"ui"} (which has a maximum of 32 characters) to be shown while loading. -2 @{"i"}string@{"ui"} causes @{"i"}string@{"ui"} (maximum 32 characters) to also be shown while loading. -b @{"i"}colour@{"ui"} specifies the border colour while loading. -g @{"i"}string@{"ui"} causes @{"i"}string@{"ui"} (maximum 32 characters) to be used as the game name while loading. -l @{"i"}string@{"ui"} causes @{"i"}string@{"ui"} (maximum 8 characters) to be used as the BASIC filename in the loader. -o @{"i"}filename@{"ui"} causes the output to be sent to @{"i"}filename@{"ui"}. -r causes the final line of attribute data in the loading screen to be bright. -s @{"i"}speed@{"ui"} specifies the speed of the loader; available values for @{"i"}speed@{"ui"} are 0 (1500 bps), 1 (2250 bps), 2 (3000 bps) and 3 (6000 bps). -v specifies verbose output. -$ @{"i"}filename@{"ui"} specifies that the ZX Spectrum screen stored in @{"i"}filename@{"ui"} should be used as the loading screen. @{"i"}snapshot@{"ui"} specifies the snapshot (in a format supported by @{" " link "'libspectrum.3'/MAIN"}@{"i"}libspectrum@{"ui"}(3) ) to be converted. 

In any @{"i"}string@{"ui"} parameter, the tilde (~) will be converted into a copyright symbol. @{" " link "'#toc4'/MAIN"}Bugs None known. @{" " link "'#toc5'/MAIN"}See Also @{" " link "'fuse.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}fuse@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'fuse-utils.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}fuse-utils@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'libspectrum.3'/MAIN"}@{"i"}libspectrum@{"ui"}(3) , @{" " link "'listbasic.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}listbasic@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'snapconv.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}snapconv@{"ui"}(1) 

The comp.sys.sinclair Spectrum FAQ, at 
@{" " link "'http://www.worldofspectrum.org/faq/index.html.guide/MAIN"}@{"i"}http://www.worldofspectrum.org/faq/index.html@{"ui"}. @{" " link "'#toc6'/MAIN"}Author Philip Kendall (philip-fuse@shadowmagic.org.uk). 

Tomaz Kac wrote @{"i"}z802tzx@{"ui"} (@{"i"}ftp://ftp.worldofspectrum.org/pub/sinclair/tools/unix/z802tzx-1.2.tar.gz@{"ui"}), on which @{"i"}snap2tzx@{"ui"} is very heavily based. 

Martijn van der Heide wrote the turbo-loading code, originally for @{"i"}Taper @{"ui"}(@{"i"}http://www.worldofspectrum.org/taper.html@{"ui"}). 


